testcase.name: Verify that the Sign up popup appears when user clicks the Sign up link
Verify that user is able to sign up when entering valid inputs in all fields
Verify that the error message is shown when user leaves the full name blank
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters data less than 6 characters
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters only spaces in the Full name field
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters email in the wrong format
Verify that the error message is shown when user leaves the email field blank
Verify that the error message is shown when user enters only spaces in the email field
Verify that the error message is shown when user leaves phone number field blank
Verify that the error message is shown when user leaves password field blank
